entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have successfully assisted Wedge Antilles in finding the Imperial Detainment Facility.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Find the crash site near the Mining Outpost on Yavin IV.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Go to the crash site near the Mining Outpost
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Search the passengers and crew for anything that might be useful.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Search the bodies of the shuttle passengers and crew to see if you can find any important intelligence.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: I've analyzed the data you sent. The shuttle's destination was the Imperial Fortress there on Yavin IV. I need you to investigate a new Detainment Facility at that location. I'm sure it is heavily guarded.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Go to the Imperial Fortress and find the Detainment Facility
entries.task05_comm_message_text: So it is true. The new facility is there. Come back to Coronet, I have a very important mission to discuss with you.
